::Mosquitor::

Running at KitKat and Stingtra, Mosquitor trips over his own foot, the Pred 
faling face first to the ground, Time Bomb's and Land Mine's shots sailing 
over his head. The bug jumps up, taking flight and firing at Time Bomb.
